text:
Archery club. Funshots and archery course provided. Bows and arrows are available for rent. Coach angie was friendly.

Do make bookingz through email from the website. Reply may take some time do be patient.

Note that it is only open during weekend from 830 to 130pm.

Awesome and fun! Really convenient for beginners.
